5aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 37, "raw_text": "37. 在這則寓言中，「這個走出洞穴後再回到洞內的人」最可能是象徵下列哪一種\n    人？\n    (A)受迫的奴隸\n    (B)孤獨的先知\n    (C)命運的主宰\n    (D)蒙昧的愚者\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-038", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據這則寓言，下列何者最接近柏拉圖的想法？", "options": ["多數人相信的事未必為真", "自以為是往往會招致滅亡", "面向陽光，影子就會在你背後", "堅定信仰，心靈才能得到自由"], "correct_answer": 0, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-36", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 38, "raw_text": "38. 根據這則寓言，下列何者最接近柏拉圖的想法？\n    (A)多數人相信的事未必為真\n    (B)自以為是往往會招致滅亡\n    (C)面向陽光，影子就會在你背後\n    (D)堅定信仰，心靈才能得到自由\n\n\n\n\n"}, "is_active": true, "auto_gradable": true, "difficulty": 3, "explanation": null}, {"id": "cap-111-chinese-039", "exam_id": "cap", "subject_id": "sub-cap-chinese", "paper_id": "cap-111-chinese", "question_type": "single_choice", "question_text": "根據甲、乙兩文推論，漢文帝時各種錢幣的重量依序最可能是下列何者？", "options": ["四銖錢 ＞ 吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢", "四銖錢 ＝ 鄧通錢 ＞ 吳錢", "吳錢 ＞ 四銖錢 ＞ 鄧通錢", "吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢 ＝ 四銖錢"], "correct_answer": 3, "correct_answer_json": null, "parent_question_id": "cap-111-chinese-passage-39", "media": null, "source": "official", "source_meta": {"parser_version": "cap_v0.1", "merger_version": "cap_merger_v0.2", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T19:26:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a6fe6a465aa1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5db25b41f664", "flags": [], "parse_confidence": 1.0, "original_question_number": 39, "raw_text": "39. 根據甲、乙兩文推論，漢文帝時各種錢幣的重量依序最可能是下列何者？\n    (A)四銖錢 ＞ 吳錢 ＞ 鄧通錢\n    (B)四銖錢 ＝ 鄧通錢 ＞ 吳錢\n    (C)吳錢 ＞ 四